{"tid":468684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金判坤不滿西亞球證執法 「作客北韓全力爭勝」","createTime":"2017-11-14T14:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T02:37:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2becb748761ede5678aa81b7e59e3db6585399","tid":468684,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510670430_e2a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510670430_e2a6.jpg&h=4f5c4aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港足球代表隊周二晚在亞洲盃外圍賽B組對黎巴嫩關鍵一戰，因陳俊樂上半場被逐兼輸12碼，10人應戰下以0:1惜敗。原本若能戰勝黎巴嫩，下場作客北韓若和波，或仍可靠得失球差取得出線權，但現在就只有擊敗北韓，才有扭轉形勢的機會。<br />\n<br />\n港隊教練金判坤賽後記者會上表示，感謝球員，在困難情況全努力付出，為香港市民而戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不滿亞洲足協安排西亞球證執法，部份球證，不能談論太多球證的執法。<br />\n<br />\n知道只有勝出對出線形勢有幫助，故Kim Sir部署此戰時沒想過和波，全力爭勝，因和波對出線形勢沒有幫助，但感謝球員付出，而作客北韓如勝出，可憑較佳對賽成績出線，但很困難，只能盡力而為。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩教練拉度洛域賽後表示：「今仗對我們來說是很困難的，早段有球員受傷，影響比賽計劃。香港亦踢得好很，我們有點運氣，當12碼出現，我們入球了，對手紅牌，比賽已經完結。」黎巴嫩隊長馬杜克就認為，陳俊樂值得領紅及輸12碼。"},{"pid":"2e6c5b8ef3d7acf841ffb5d401566f7e08c300cb","tid":468684,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:11:29.000Z","msg":"下場係北韓打:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b1446883efa0187f7ba60b4e334c7b87820b2","tid":468684,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:17:05.000Z","msg":"好似有中立場<br />\n<br />\n北韓唔會比Kim sir入境呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c985bab566bdb6f56f49fba8f7bfa4853e95f3bd","tid":468684,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似有中立場<br />\n<br />\n北韓唔會比Kim sir入境呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾個月香港先作客和咗北泡喎，kim 入到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc9060a26156e72c5b16bd580087b52a4872131","tid":468684,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似有中立場<br />\n<br />\n北韓唔會比Kim sir入境呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾個月香港先作客和咗北泡喎，kim 入到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nu18?"},{"pid":"fbc1e91ba3b7e92ce5ac34c60d7d3f005b492cc6","tid":468684,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似有中立場<br />\n<br />\n北韓唔會比Kim sir入境呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾個月香港先作客和咗北泡喎，kim 入到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nu18?</blockquote><br />\n望就望金仔射幾炮過南泡海面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再唔係試射導彈但飛錯方向去鴨綠江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab0cf6a0f89247c79be879f7fec0892eb100cb6","tid":468684,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"賤種西亞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2975f1b7ee536c92d138f0c7e01a2835873c2450","tid":468684,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似有中立場<br />\n<br />\n北韓唔會比Kim sir入境呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾個月香港先作客和咗北泡喎，kim 入到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nu18?</blockquote><br />\nu22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96958550f9ff0ad61c005